: "289 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/467798045"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Isu27m6fZisR/EAMaCDY2MjM0NjU1IIbd2oYGMA84zQJADHIJNDY3Nzk4MDQ1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1624705303.2841723", "card_id": "Q_466845525", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 54}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "我国新冠疫苗接种剂次超 10 亿，是否达到全民免疫，对比世界其他国家是什么水平？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据国家卫健委 20 日通报，截至 2021 年 6 月 19 日，31 个省（自治区、直辖市）和新疆生产建设兵团累计报告接种新冠病毒疫苗超 10 亿剂次。中国疫苗的接种速度纷纷引来外媒关注。 从 2020 年 12 月 15 日正式开展重点人群接种工作以来，中国的新冠疫苗接种速度不断提高，从 1 亿剂次到 10 亿剂次，每增加 1 亿剂次接种所需时间不断缩短。从接种 1 亿剂次到超过 2 亿剂次，历时 25 天；从 2 亿剂次到 3 亿剂次，用了 16 天；而从 4 亿剂次以后，每新增 1 亿剂次的天数不超过一周，从接种 9 亿剂次到超过 10 亿剂次，只用了 5 天时间。 从最新的各国疫苗总接种量来看，全球合计疫苗接种量已接近 25 亿剂次，中国接种总量就超过 10 亿剂次，位居全球第一，占全球总量的比例超 40%。美国排在第二位，总接种量超过 3 亿剂；印度排在第三，总接种量为 2.5 亿剂。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-cd4664fdef60339bc86e20bd61d6a9f7_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "286 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/466845525"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Isu27m6fZisR/EAMaCDY2MDIyNzc3IN+azIYGMAc4pwJADXIJNDY2ODQ1NTI1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1624705303.2847328", "card_id": "Q_35296900", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1312}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "Steam 上有哪些必买游戏？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "价格不限，类型不限。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-8eeaa7cc3b9e52db63166e1a15c2ba7a_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "269 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/35296900"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Isu27m6fZisR/EAMaBzYzMjUzNzQg3/efrwUwKTiwsANADnIIMzUyOTY5MDB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_fe